   <text type="translation">
      <body>
         <pb facs="1865_05_14_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_Pandel_Stiehaus_Batavia_1.tif" n="envelope"/>
         <p>By steamer via<lb/>Singapore +Shanghai.<lb/>P.O.S. A.N.V. SUEZ
                PAOF<lb/>27<lb/>AVRIL<lb/>65<lb/>IMPER <lb/>BATAVIA<lb/>14/5<lb/>1865 <lb/>Messrs.
                L. Kniffler + Co.<lb/>FRANCO<lb/>PANDEL &amp;
                STIEHAUS<lb/>BATAVIA<lb/>Yokohama<lb/>INDIA PAID<lb/>BY
                BATAVIA<lb/>Japan<lb/>⟨1865<lb/>Pandel &amp; Stiehaus<lb/>Batavia 14th
                May<lb/>Answered 26th June⟩</p>
         <pb facs="1865_05_14_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_Pandel_Stiehaus_Batavia_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <p>PANDEL &amp; STIEHAUS <lb/>BATAVIA Batavia May 14th 1865<lb/>By steamer
                via<lb/>Singapore + Shanghai<lb/>Messrs.<lb/>L. Kniffler + Co.<lb/>Yokohama<lb/>We
                are confirming our respectful last letter from 29th April,<lb/>of which a press-copy
                is enclosed &amp; have since been without <lb/>any of your esteemed letters.
                <lb/>The business appears to be getting a little <lb/>more lively, our purchasers
                can be<lb/>seen more often &amp; put in offers on goods which have been
                <lb/>neglected for a long time. <lb/>The demand for ginghams + cottonettes is
                holding up<lb/> &amp; well-assorted selections are easy to sell at <lb/>good prices.
                For staple goods demand<lb/>remains limited &amp; sales can only be managed
                at<lb/>low prices. Drills are recorded at<lb/> f 13 to 14 6/4, white madapollam f 10
                „_ „ 5/4 f. f. 8¼ 6/4, calico<lb/> f 10 ½ to f 11 - f 5/4 f 8 ½ to f 9,-. For Jap.
                wares<lb/>there is no demand at the moment, we believe, however, <lb/>that, if a
                well-assorted shipment arrives here in a short <lb/>while, this will be able to be
                sold easily and at a profit. <lb/>In the export business it is quiet &amp; there are
                only few products<lb/>on the market, the details as well as the state of cargoes
                &amp; rates <lb/>we ask you to gather from our enclosed report.<lb/>In deep
                friendship<lb/>Pandel + Stiehaus</p>
         <pb facs="1865_05_14_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_Pandel_Stiehaus_Batavia_3.tif" n="3"/>
         <pb facs="1865_05_14_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_Pandel_Stiehaus_Batavia_4.tif" n="4"/>
      </body>
   </text>
